column5: Hey, anyone up for some fishing tonight? I'm probably heading down to pier 4, by the yacht club, unless a better idea comes up. I'll be heading down about 6 or so. If anyone wants to join me, send a PM.
why not go fisherman's pier try for some salmon if youre going at night
Cause I have no idea what I'm doing there, lol. At least when it comes to salmon fishing. I don't know about lures, if my line or even if my rod can handle it. Soon, though.
Anyway, here's one of what I landed tonight, along with 9 Gobies.
